        "canon_role": "section_header",
        "text": "附子",
        "bbox": [
          0.4738858626273595,
          0.14306152299540886,
          0.5444646081250513,
          0.16009265668533848
        ],
        "order": 2
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129_2",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "【来源】毛茛科植物乌头的子根的加工品。",
        "bbox": [
          0.15880217736980662,
          0.16690511016131032,
          0.49405121848384287,
          0.18393624385123994
        ],
        "order": 3
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129_6",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "",
        "bbox": [
          0.5772333113918368,
          0.17031133689929626,
          0.8948376661314501,
          0.3218884267396699
        ],
        "order": 4
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129_3",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "【采收加工】夏秋季采挖，除去主根、须根及泥 沙，习称“泥附子”。以不同的方法加工制成盐附 子、黑顺片、白附片直接入药。",
        "bbox": [
          0.1209921351389003,
          0.18734247058922587,
          0.5570679555353534,
          0.2452483251349866
        ],
        "order": 5
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129_4",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "【质量标志】盐附子以个大、体重、色灰黄、表 面起盐霜者为佳。黑顺片以片大、厚薄均匀、切面油 润有光泽者为佳。白附片以片大、色白、油润、半透 明者为佳。水分不得超过15%。",
        "bbox": [
          0.1209921351389003,
          0.24865455187297253,
          0.5570679555353534,
          0.3269977668466488
        ],
        "order": 6
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129_5",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "【饮片特征】①盐附子：呈圆锥形，顶端凹陷， 福",
        "bbox": [
          0.13863682151332324,
          0.33040399358463474,
          0.5495059470891721,
          0.3474351272745643
        ],
        "order": 7
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129_7",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "高5～8cm。表面黑褐色，粗糙，附有盐粒结晶，可见突起的支根及支根痕，断面色略淡，有 1个多角形环纹。体重，质稍坚。气微，味咸而麻舌。②黑顺片（图2-168）：为纵切片，上宽 下窄，长1.7~5cm，宽0.9～3cm，厚0.2~0.5cm。外皮黑褐色，切面暗黄色，油润且具光 泽，呈半透明状，并有纵向导管束。质硬而脆，断面呈角质样。气微，味淡。③白附片：无残留 外皮，呈黄白色，半透明，厚约0.3 cm。",
        "bbox": [
          0.1209921351389003,
          0.3508413540125503,
          0.899879005095571,
          0.4496219294141421
        ],
        "order": 8
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129_8",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "【贮藏要求】置干燥处，防潮。",
        "bbox": [
          0.15880217736980662,
          0.45302815615212805,
          0.4033071171296676,
          0.47005928984205764
        ],
        "order": 9
      }
    ]
  },
