        "canon_role": "section_header",
        "text": "肉桂",
        "bbox": [
          0.4764065321094199,
          0.4802779700560154,
          0.5444646081250513,
          0.49730910374594506
        ],
        "order": 10
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129_10",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "【来源】樟科植物肉桂的树皮。",
        "bbox": [
          0.15880217736980662,
          0.5041215572219169,
          0.4007864476476072,
          0.5211526909118466
        ],
        "order": 11
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129_15",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "",
        "bbox": [
          0.5747126419097763,
          0.5092308973288958,
          0.8973583356135105,
          0.6608079871692695
        ],
        "order": 12
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129_11",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "【采收加工】一般在秋季剥取，阴干。",
        "bbox": [
          0.15880217736980662,
          0.5245589176498324,
          0.45876184573499695,
          0.5415900513397621
        ],
        "order": 13
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129_12",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "【质量标志】药材以皮细而坚实，肉厚而沉重， 断面紫红色，油性足，香气浓，辛、甜味大，嚼之无 渣者为佳。水分不得超过15%，总灰分不得超过5%。",
        "bbox": [
          0.1209921351389003,
          0.544996278077748,
          0.5570679555353534,
          0.6029021326235087
        ],
        "order": 14
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129_13",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "【饮片特征】呈不规则的板状或卷筒状，厚 0.2～0.8cm。外表面呈灰棕色，有的可见灰白色斑 纹。内表面呈红棕色，较平坦，有细纵纹，划处显油 痕。质硬，断面不平坦，外层呈棕色、较粗糙，内 层呈红棕色，有油润感，两层间可见1条黄棕色的线 纹。气香浓烈，味甜、辣。（图2-169)",
        "bbox": [
          0.1209921351389003,
          0.6063083593614946,
          0.5595886250174138,
          0.725526295191002
        ],
        "order": 15
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129_14",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "【贮藏要求】置阴凉且干燥处。",
        "bbox": [
          0.15880217736980662,
          0.7323387486669739,
          0.4033071171296676,
          0.7493698823569035
        ],
        "order": 16
      }
    ]
  },
