        "text": "干姜",
        "bbox": [
          0.4764065321094199,
          0.7578854492018683,
          0.5444646081250513,
          0.774916582891798
        ],
        "order": 17
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129_17",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "【来源】姜科植物姜的根茎。",
        "bbox": [
          0.15880217736980662,
          0.7834321497367628,
          0.3831417612731842,
          0.7987601700576994
        ],
        "order": 18
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129_18",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "【采收加工】冬季采收，去掉须根和泥沙，晒干或者低温干燥。趁鲜进行切片晒干或低温干 燥者称为“干姜”。",
        "bbox": [
          0.11595079617477945,
          0.8038695101646783,
          0.899879005095571,
          0.8396348909135305
        ],
        "order": 19
      }
